<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">


<Paragraph FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">
This sample illustrates document editor using RichTextBoxAdv control that is similar to Microsoft Word 2003 version with tool bar and menu options.
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">
The following screenshot displays the same.
</Paragraph>
<Paragraph TextAlignment ="Center"><Image Source="Images\CustomizedToolBar.png" Stretch="None" /></Paragraph>   

<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}" FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">Features</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<List FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports to view, print and edit Word, HTML, XAML and text documents.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports undo and redo editing operations.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports cut, copy, and paste the text to and from the RichTextBoxAdv.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports to restrict user editing.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports context menu and shortcut keys for all necessary editing operations.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports commands that can be used for XAML command binding with UI elements.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>
</FlowDocument>